      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even sleep anymore. every time i look at the news or even just look out the window i feel like everything is just... over. like we're all just watching the clock run out on the planet and there's nothing anyone can actually do. it feels so stupid to even try to plan a future or care about anything when the world is literally dying.",
